      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle is a practical choice for a handy buyer, first-time driver, or anyone seeking inexpensive transportation. Offered at an appealing price, it presents a solid opportunity for basic driving needs, a project, or extra utility without a major investment. A straightforward value purchase with room to make it your own.",
