    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little car with plenty of life left for the right buyer. It\u2019s not a showpiece, but it\u2019s a straightforward, affordable option if you need cheap wheels, a handy runabout, or a solid project to tinker with. Easy on the wallet and priced to sell, with the kind of character only a well-used car can earn. If you\u2019re after something simple and budget-friendly, this could be a great fit.",
      "price": 5900.0,
