      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project car with strong enthusiast appeal and plenty of usable life left for the right buyer. The motor starts, runs, and delivers the kind of honest mechanical feel that makes these cars worth saving, with a drivetrain that still shows good character. It\u2019s not a showroom piece, but it has the right bones for a budget daily, weekend wrenching project, or parts donor with upside. If you know your way around maintenance and don\u2019t mind cosmetic or age-related needs, this is an affordable entry point with real potential.",
      "price": 5900.0,
